### Selection Helpers

-   `starts_with()`/`ends_with()`

-   `contains()`

-   `matches()`

-   `everything()`

-   `all_of()`

-   `any_of()`

-   `where()`

`contains()` example.

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
cereal1 %>%
  select(contains("_rating")) 
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
